The paper deals with linear precoding in multi-user MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a new precoding scheme that reduces the gap between per-stream effective channel gains, which is a problem related to signal processing (cs.SI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with multi-stream transmission, which is a topic related to multimedia systems (cs.MM).
